User Module API Documentation
Base URL
/api/users
Authentication
Tất cả API yêu cầu JWT Token.
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
Role yêu cầu:
ROLE_USER

1. Get My Profile
Lấy thông tin hồ sơ của sinh viên đang đăng nhập.
Endpoint
GET /api/users/me
Authorization
ROLE_USER

Request Header
Authorization: Bearer <token>

Response Success
Status Code
200 OK
Response Body
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Get profile successfully",
  "data": {
    "id": 1,
    "username": "student01",
    "role": "USER",
    "studentCode": "SV001",
    "fullName": "Nguyễn Văn A",
    "cccd": "079204005678",
    "gender": "MALE",
    "dateOfBirth": "2004-01-15",
    "phone": "0912345678",
    "email": "vana@example.com",
    "faculty": "Information Technology",
    "course": "K20",
    "avatarUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/avatar.jpg"
  }
}

Error Responses
Unauthorized
401 Unauthorized
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Unauthorized"
}
Student Profile Not Found
404 Not Found
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Student profile not found"
}

2. Update Profile
Cập nhật thông tin cá nhân sinh viên.
Endpoint
PUT /api/users/me
Authorization
ROLE_USER

Request Header
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

Request Body
Example
{
  "fullName": "Nguyễn Văn B",
  "phone": "0987654321",
  "email": "vanb@example.com"
}

Validation Rules
Field	Type	Required	Validation
fullName	String	No	Nếu gửi thì không được rỗng
phone	String	No	Đúng định dạng số điện thoại VN
email	String	No	Đúng định dạng email

Phone Regex
(84|0[3|5|7|8|9])+([0-9]{8})

Response Success
Status Code
200 OK
Response Body
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Profile updated successfully",
  "data": null
}

Error Responses
Invalid Phone Number
400 Bad Request
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Invalid phone number"
}
Invalid Email
400 Bad Request
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Invalid email"
}
Email Already Exists
400 Bad Request
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Email already exists"
}
Student Not Found
404 Not Found
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Student not found"
}

3. Upload Avatar
Upload ảnh đại diện sinh viên.
Endpoint
POST /api/users/me/avatar
Authorization
ROLE_USER
Content Type
multipart/form-data

Request Header
Authorization: Bearer <token>

Form Data
Key	Type	Required	Description
file	MultipartFile	Yes	File ảnh avatar

Example Request
form-data
KEY	VALUE	TYPE
file	avatar.png	File

Response Success
Status Code
200 OK
Response Body
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Avatar updated successfully",
  "data": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dormitory/avatar.jpg"
}

Error Responses
No File Uploaded
400 Bad Request
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "No file uploaded"
}
Student Not Found
404 Not Found
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Student not found"
}
Upload Failed
500 Internal Server Error
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Failed to upload avatar"
}

Entity: Student
Field	Type	Constraint
id	Long	Primary Key
studentCode	String	Unique
avatarUrl	String	Nullable
fullName	String
cccd	String	Unique, Not Null
dateOfBirth	LocalDate
gender	ENUM	Not Null
phone	String
email	String	Unique
faculty	String
course	String

Notes
API sử dụng JWT Authentication.
Avatar upload bằng Cloudinary.
CCCD là định danh duy nhất của sinh viên.
Email phải unique trong hệ thống.
Chỉ tài khoản có role USER mới được truy cập API.
